# A configuration file for Imfit that specifies a Sersic, a FerrersBar2D and Exponential model for Au-06NoR #

ORIGINAL_SKY 82.46

X0      256.00      254,258
Y0      256.00      254,258

FUNCTION Sersic
PA      90          0,180
ell     0.0         0,1
n       0.1
I_e     89
r_e     158

FUNCTION FerrersBar2D
PA      90          0,180
ell     0.2         0,0.4
c0      0.5         0,0.8
n       2           0,2
I_0     25          10,50
a_bar   10          5,10

FUNCTION Exponential
PA      180         0,180
ell     0.0         0,0.2
I_0     178
h       376

